column5: Well JMH and his Brother ...the 1st group back in today did well fished from day light to 9:30..way to go guys nice Eye's for 2 1/2 hours of fishing ..
Nice grand river walleyes guys well done !!!!...nice pic too...cheers

What a start to hard water  fishing ! Lots of walleye caught today of all sizes with some big girls released . Seemed everyone was having good luck today and what a beautiful day for fishing !I even skipped out front  for a hour before dark ...and as soon as I dropped the vex in 13 fow  spotted fish .it  wasn’t long before  I had 3 on the ice with the guy beside me leaving  before dark with his limit in 30 min . Buck Shots and Rapala  Jigs tipped with shinners  were the ticket…
Good Job guys!! nice fish!  I better hurry up and renew my outdoors card.
